{"article_id":"Cv545EZwEA9OMrZ3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Iowa Democratic Party :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"App 'Coding Issue ' To Blame For Delay In Caucus Results","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"The Iowa caucuses are n't over yet .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"A delay in the results meant the state Democratic Party did not call the race Monday night","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"as expected ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"leaving the candidates and their supporters in limbo .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"State party officials said Tuesday morning","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"they are certain","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"`` the underlying data ''","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"collected at caucus sites","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"is sound","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"but that an issue arose","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"in reporting that data .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Results are expected later Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Chair Troy Price said","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"though the app was recording data accurately ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"`` it was reporting out only partial data ''","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"because of a `` coding issue in the reporting system . ''","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"NPR 's Miles Parks previously reported on concerns over the new use of a smartphone app","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"for reporting results .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"As campaigns and caucusgoers anxiously awaited results last night ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Price had said","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"the party is `` manually verifying all precinct results ''","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"and expects to have numbers sometime Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"`` We are validating every piece of data","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"we have","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"against our paper trail , ''","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Price said .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"`` That system is taking longer","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"than expected ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"but it 's in place","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"to ensure","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"we are eventually able to report results with full confidence . ''","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"The party said","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"`` inconsistencies '' were found in a few results sets","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"but that the delay was not caused by a `` a hack or intrusion . ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"But multiple county chairs on the ground blamed malfunctions , including on the app","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"used to report results .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` We found inconsistencies in the reporting of three sets of results .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"In addition to the tech systems","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"being used","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"to tabulate results ,","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"we are also using photos of results and a paper trail","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"to validate","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"that all results match","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"and ensure","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"that we have confidence and accuracy in the numbers","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"we report , ''","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"Iowa Democratic Party Communications Director Mandy McClure said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"`` This is simply a reporting issue ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"the app did not go down","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"and this is not a hack or an intrusion , ''","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"McClure continued .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"`` The underlying data and paper trail is sound","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and will simply take time","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"to further report the results . ''","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Multiple county chairs on Monday night told NPR","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"that there were , in fact , malfunctions","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that delayed reporting .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"`` The app did n't work .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Things did n't work out right .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"I 've been trying to call for several hours","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"to report my results , ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Des Moines County Democratic Party Co-Chairman Tom Courtney told NPR .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"`` And I ca n't get through the phone .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"It 's a phone number","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"and I ca n't get through .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"That number is constantly busy . ''","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Instead , Courtney said","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"he went home","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and planned to call","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and report his precinct 's results in the morning .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"`` [ The Iowa Democratic Party ] made it seem like this was going to work fine .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"They tested it ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"tested it , ''","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Courtney said .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"`` I 'm old enough ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"I was skeptical , the whole thing ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"but I thought","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"it would be better","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"than it is .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"There have been problems .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Little problems with it , right , all along .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Guess","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"I was n't surprised . ''","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Kurt Meyer , the chairman of the Tri-County Democrats","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"( three rural counties in northern Iowa ) ,","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"echoed Courtney 's frustrations .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"`` There has been a lot of concerns from the get-go about the security of the system .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Why ?","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Well , because we know","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that there are plenty of interests","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"that would just as soon thwart the accurate reporting of results .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"So as a result , security has been a major issue , ''","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Meyer said .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"`` And yet the security of the system becomes an issue","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"in part","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"because you have all these volunteers in 1,700 different precincts ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"a lot of the volunteers are not going to be technologically sophisticated . ''","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"As several candidates went ahead","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"and addressed their restless supporters overnight ,","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"there was a mounting frustration among the campaigns , too .","depth":4},{"id":102,"text":"The Iowa Democratic Party and Democratic presidential campaigns held a phone call","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"as the delay became clear","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"sources say","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"became heated at times .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"Dana Remus , campaign general counsel to former Vice President Joe Biden , sent a letter to Price and IDP Executive Director Kevin Geiken","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"demanding `` full explanations and relevant information ''","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"after what the Biden campaign calls `` failed '' systems and `` considerable flaws '' by the IDP","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"deployed for tonight 's caucuses .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"`` The app","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"that was intended to relay Caucus results to the Party","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"failed ;","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"the Party 's back-up telephonic reporting system likewise has failed .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Now , we understand","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"that Caucus Chairs are attempting to","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"- and , in many cases , failing to -","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"report results telephonically to the Party .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"These acute failures are occurring statewide , ''","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Remus said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":241,"left":122,"right":240,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":218,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":218,"left":175,"right":217,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":125,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":2,"right":124,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":5,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":132,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":131,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":6,"right":130,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":128,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":7,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":150,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":137,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":135,"right":136,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":14,"right":134,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":133,"right":17,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":136,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":140,"r